==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Privately
<hw>Pri"vate*ly</hw> <pr>(pr⟦imac⟧"v⟦asl⟧t*l⟦ycr⟧)</pr>,
<pos>adv.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>In a private manner; not openly; without the
presence of others.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In a manner affecting an individual; personally; not
officially; <as>as, he is not <ex>privately</ex>
benefited</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Privateness</ent>⟦br⟧
